Sochi 2014 Winter Olympics: Closing Ceremony
Live coverage as the 22nd Winter Olympic Games come to a close after 16 days of sporting highlights. The spectacular closing ceremony celebrates Sochi's hosting of the Games, and as the Olympic flame is extinguished in the Fisht Stadium, thoughts will turn to the next Winter Olympics in Pyeongchang in South Korea in 2018. Commentary by Hazel Irvine.
